text_Basalt: A smooth looking rock which again is up against a rock with a lot of spots all over.
text_Diorite: Has little spots all over. These seem to be mainly black and sprinkled around. Probably would feel very rough in hand.

text_Pegmatite: These look like what you think the average gem stones would look like. They have that solid black spot that makes me think of a gem stone.
text_Pumice: These rocks have little holes all around and look like they would feel very smooth if touched.
